Interesting options for curl :

# Change Method
-X POST

# Add a HTTP header
--header "Content-Type: application/oms"

# Post Data
--data "<root>some datas</root>"
--data-binary @FILENAME

#----------------------

# Use a cookie
--cookie "session=1b7607ea628b66369c555da95d090de6|session2.th2|3"

# Avoid warning for certificate
--insecure

#----------------------

# Pass through a proxy
--proxy "host.com:3128"

# Pass through socks5
--socks5 127.0.0.1:9999
